-- Real product photos for 199 notable beers that had none: pulled from each
-- beer's Wikidata item (P18) as a Wikimedia Commons Special:FilePath URL, all
-- free-licensed. Only fills rows that are still imageless (no cutout, no label),
-- so nothing is overwritten. Verified: every QID returned a real image from the
-- Wikidata Query Service (77% of the notable imageless set); the rest genuinely
-- have no free image and keep the style glass. No fabrication.

